sourcesContent:
export const QUESTIONS_ZH = [
  // 一、灵活应变（Cognitive Flexibility）
  { id: 1, text: "我适应计划变更，并尝试其他解决方式。", category: "Cognitive Flexibility" },
  { id: 2, text: "我可以从休闲顺利切换到学习任务。", category: "Cognitive Flexibility" },
  { id: 3, text: "我在面对难题时会尝试用不同方法来解决。", category: "Cognitive Flexibility" },
  { id: 4, text: "我愿意听取与我不同的意见。", category: "Cognitive Flexibility" },
  { id: 5, text: "我能灵活看待问题，不拘泥于一种想法。", category: "Cognitive Flexibility" },
  { id: 6, text: "我面对新情况能快速调整应对方式。", category: "Cognitive Flexibility" },

  // 二、元认知（Metacognition）
  { id: 7, text: "我清楚自己在哪些方面擅长，哪些方面需要努力。", category: "Metacognition" },
  { id: 8, text: "我在开始任务前，会思考最有效的完成方法。", category: "Metacognition" },
  { id: 9, text: "我能在任务进行中调整策略以提高效果。", category: "Metacognition" },
  { id: 10, text: "我完成任务后，会反思哪些地方还能改进。", category: "Metacognition" },
  { id: 11, text: "我能意识到自己的情绪对任务表现的影响。", category: "Metacognition" },
  { id: 12, text: "我知道哪些习惯能帮助我更好地完成任务。", category: "Metacognition" },

  // 三、工作记忆（Working Memory）
  { id: 13, text: "我能记住多步指令并依次完成。", category: "Working Memory" },
  { id: 14, text: "我听故事时能记住关键内容。", category: "Working Memory" },
  { id: 15, text: "我能记住刚学的内容并用上它。", category: "Working Memory" },
  { id: 16, text: "我做事很少因为忘记细节而中断。", category: "Working Memory" },
  { id: 17, text: "我能同时处理多个任务的信息。", category: "Working Memory" },
  { id: 18, text: "我读文章时能记住重要内容而不是逐句忘记。", category: "Working Memory" },

  // 四、组织能力（Organization）
  { id: 19, text: "我的东西摆放整齐，容易找到。", category: "Organization" },
  { id: 20, text: "我准备好所需材料后再开始任务。", category: "Organization" },
  { id: 21, text: "我安排任务时考虑先后顺序。", category: "Organization" },
  { id: 22, text: "我有计划地做事，不慌乱。", category: "Organization" },
  { id: 23, text: "我的书包、抽屉通常很整洁。", category: "Organization" },
  { id: 24, text: "我做事情时有清晰的步骤和流程。", category: "Organization" },

  // 五、情绪调节（Emotional Regulation）
  { id: 25, text: "我在不开心时能找到方法让自己冷静。", category: "Emotional Regulation" },
  { id: 26, text: "我面对批评或失败时能逐渐恢复平静。", category: "Emotional Regulation" },
  { id: 27, text: "我能表达情绪，而不是闷在心里。", category: "Emotional Regulation" },
  { id: 28, text: "我知道情绪会影响任务表现。", category: "Emotional Regulation" },
  { id: 29, text: "我在紧张场合能控制情绪不失控。", category: "Emotional Regulation" },
  { id: 30, text: "我遇到不顺利时，能鼓励自己继续努力。", category: "Emotional Regulation" },

  // 六、自我约束（Inhibitory Control）
  { id: 31, text: "我做决定前会考虑后果。", category: "Inhibitory & Impulse Control" },
  { id: 32, text: "我学习时能控制自己不被打断。", category: "Inhibitory & Impulse Control" },
  { id: 33, text: "我能坚持完成任务后再休息。", category: "Inhibitory & Impulse Control" },
  { id: 34, text: "我不会因为冲动而打断别人说话或活动。", category: "Inhibitory & Impulse Control" },
  { id: 35, text: "我能抑制想做但不合适的行为。", category: "Inhibitory & Impulse Control" },
  { id: 36, text: "我面对诱惑时能坚持完成重要任务。", category: "Inhibitory & Impulse Control" },

  // 七、自驱力（Task Initiation & Motivation）
  { id: 37, text: "我不等别人提醒就主动开始任务。", category: "Task Initiation & Motivation" },
  { id: 38, text: "我相信努力可以帮助我达成目标。", category: "Task Initiation & Motivation" },
  { id: 39, text: "我面对挑战时不会轻易放弃。", category: "Task Initiation & Motivation" },
  { id: 40, text: "我即使不喜欢任务也能启动行动。", category: "Task Initiation & Motivation" },
  { id: 41, text: "我会设定目标并努力实现。", category: "Task Initiation & Motivation" },
  { id: 42, text: "我做事充满动力，不容易中途停下。", category: "Task Initiation & Motivation" },

  // 八、注意力维持（Sustained Attention）
  { id: 43, text: "我可以长时间专注做一件事。", category: "Sustained Attention" },
  { id: 44, text: "我在有干扰的环境中也能保持注意力。", category: "Sustained Attention" },
  { id: 45, text: "我做完一件事再开始下一件。", category: "Sustained Attention" },
  { id: 46, text: "我很少走神，需要提醒才能集中。", category: "Sustained Attention" },
  { id: 47, text: "我注意力一旦分散，很快能重新集中。", category: "Sustained Attention" },
  { id: 48, text: "我完成任务过程中很少分心。", category: "Sustained Attention" },

  // 九、时间管理（Time Management）
  { id: 49, text: "我按时完成任务，因为我知道时间宝贵。", category: "Time Management" },
  { id: 50, text: "我能合理安排一天的学习和休息时间。", category: "Time Management" },
  { id: 51, text: "我做事时会优先安排重要的任务。", category: "Time Management" },
  { id: 52, text: "我能准确估计完成任务所需的时间。", category: "Time Management" },
  { id: 53, text: "我不拖延任务到最后一刻。", category: "Time Management" },
  { id: 54, text: "我能根据时间安排做出合理调整。", category: "Time Management" }
];

export const CATEGORIES_ZH = {
  "Cognitive Flexibility": "灵活应变",
  "Metacognition": "元认知", 
  "Working Memory": "工作记忆",
  "Organization": "组织能力",
  "Emotional Regulation": "情绪调节",
  "Inhibitory & Impulse Control": "自我约束",
  "Task Initiation & Motivation": "自驱力",
  "Sustained Attention": "注意力维持",
  "Time Management": "时间管理"
};
